node.text: For over 3 years now I’ve had a collectible product company called @elitecoinageco (what is life!) and we’ve been working round the clock to create a collectible note that features some of the best loved TV shows, incorporated with bank note grade security AND infused with precious metals. It’s been a journey!! But I’m so glad I’m on it. So ladies & gents here it is, and our first release is the officially licensed Golden Girls collectible note. This is a unique and incredible memento infused with 24K gold, with museum-grade quality and world-class security. Watch the video (and you’ll see a few familiar faces on there lol!) to hear all about the features, and go to the website to see the Golden Girls note! Yes I’m tagging @bettywhite. Official release is July 22nd but you can reserve yours right now for a limited time introductory price! Go to elitecoinage.com or the link in my bio. THANKS SO MUCH LOVES!

node.text: Decided to post this #DWTS rehearsal video of @vanderjames & I dancing our contemporary! This was on a Friday before the Monday show. James’ lovely parents were there this week as well as his ever living wife (@vanderkimberly) so this dance was dedicated to them. The lift towards the end where I’m essentially flying took some working out! There’s a special grip you need and we were so happy we worked it out!! I loved this dance and to say I was mesmerized by the way James danced it is a understatement. Hope you like this raw rehearsal footage!! #teamvanderslate @dancingabc

node.text: I will always love the way you danced this @vanderjames, and throughout the many dances I’ve done on @dancingabc, this one really will be one of my favorites. I’m so proud of you James! What did you guys think of our dance last night?! Let me know!!! And thank you thank you so so much for voting and keeping us here. So much love ❤️ also... please take a moment to appreciate the MIND BLOWING voice of @travisgarland. His voice is like nothing I’ve ever heard before 🙏🏻

node.text: For over 3 years now I’ve had a collectible product company called @elitecoinageco (what is life!) and we’ve been working round the clock to create a collectible note that features some of the best loved TV shows, incorporated with bank note grade security AND infused with precious metals. It’s been a journey!! But I’m so glad I’m on it. So ladies & gents here it is, and our first release is the officially licensed Golden Girls collectible note. This is a unique and incredible memento infused with 24K gold, with museum-grade quality and world-class security. Watch the video (and you’ll see a few familiar faces on there lol!) to hear all about the features, and go to the website to see the Golden Girls note! Yes I’m tagging @bettywhite. Official release is July 22nd but you can reserve yours right now for a limited time introductory price! Go to elitecoinage.com or the link in my bio. THANKS SO MUCH LOVES!

node.text:
Ok I wasn’t going to write this post but I had a really interesting thing happen to me today and I wanted to share. It started yesterday, speaking with my dear friend @camilladallerup about how frustrated I was about not achieving certain things that I wanted for my business - my real estate business. In her wisdom (she has endless!) she told me to write down in a notepad what I wanted my business day to look like. She said be specific! Write down what type of agent I wanted to be, how busy I wanted to be, how many connections I wanted to make and what type of professional I wanted to be for my clients. Speaking openly, she had me map out what my future real estate business looked like. So I did that. And today... nothing happened. No just kidding!!!! 
Today everything happened! I had 6 phones calls from potential new clients, both buyers & sellers, I had two wonderful meetings, met 5 realtors who are all kicking arse and I may have made the decision to join a fantastic real estate team within my brokerage. Please don’t think I’m spilling all of this to brag IN ANY WAY, that’s not my intention at all! I’m giving you specifics because I got specific with my requests on paper. I felt the power and I guess the magic of asking for what I wanted. When I excitedly shared my day’s events with my friend Cam, she responded in a way I couldn’t have put better - ‘So many are afraid of actually asking for what they want. We have to get clear so that the universe can deliver. Set the inner dial, become the magnet.’ 
I wanted to share it with you in case this is something that could help you as much as it helped me 💕
